text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha ao mnoussa lok. brasen bae puok anak meankar sangsay ampi sasanea robsakhnhom ku khnhom min korp sakkar champoh avei del puok anak korp sakkar phe sa ng pi a l laoh noh laey . kabonde khnhom korp sakkar champoh a l laoh del trong chea anak b pea ch b chivit robsa puok anak . haey khnhom trauv ban ke bangkeab brae aoy sthet knongchamnaom anak del mean chomnue
